<h2>⭐ Move the Cat Eyes 👀</h2>
<p>Use the code from the cat sample above and make its eyes move:</p>
<p><img src="samples/forloops/img/cat.gif" alt="Black cat with moving yellow eyes" /></p>
<details>
  <summary>Hint</summary>
  <p>
    Wrap the whole cat drawing in a <code>for</code> loop and modify the <code>// eyes</code> block:
  </p>
  <pre><code class="language-evy">for x := range 1000
  // ...
  // eyes
  offset := x % 12 / 8
  move 31+offset 70
  circle 2
  move 49+offset 70
  // ...
end
</code></pre>
</details>
